  "explanation": "The volume of a sphere is $V = \\frac{4}{3}\\pi r^3$. The diameter is 12 inches, so the radius is $r = 6$ inches. $V = \\frac{4}{3}\\pi(6)^3 = \\frac{4}{3}\\pi(216) = 288\\pi$ cubic inches. The answer is A.",
